## Configuration

Copy the environment template and set your application's base URL:

```bash
cp .env.example src/config/.env
```

Edit `src/config/.env`:

```env
URL=https://your-application.example.com
TEST_ENV=<%- environments.default %>
USERID=your-test-username
PASSWORD=your-test-password
LOG_LEVEL=info
```

> **Never commit `src/config/.env`** — it is gitignored. It may contain credentials.

